-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;">*판매&nbsp;회원분들은&nbsp;물품등록&nbsp;시&nbsp;위&nbsp;시간대에&nbsp;경매가&nbsp;종료되지&nbsp;않도록&nbsp;시간&nbsp;설정에&nbsp;유의해&nbsp;주시기&nbsp;바라며,</span><br style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;">*</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: Dotum, gulim;">점검이&nbsp;진행되는&nbsp;동안&nbsp;종료되는 경매는&nbsp;경매 종료시간이&nbsp;1시간&nbsp;연장 처리될&nbsp;예정입니다.</span><br style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;"><br style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;">더욱&nbsp;안정된&nbsp;환경을&nbsp;제공할&nbsp;수&nbsp;있도록&nbsp;노력하겠습니다.</span><br style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(123, 118, 118); font-family: Dotum, gulim;">감사합니다.</span><br></p>', '2018-10-18 20:42:15', '2018-10-18 20:42:15');
